LibraryItemTypeString Property

Requires: Base Development System

Class: ProjectItem Properties (ActiveX)

Returns the type of the LabVIEW project item as it exists in the project library as a string. Use the LibraryItemType property to return the type as a GUID.

This property is valid only if the LabVIEW project item exists in a project library.

Syntax

object.LibraryItemTypeString

Data Type

string
